And what did you say?

11:36.613 --> 11:39.698
Oh, you did not.

11:39.740 --> 11:43.077
Discord, why are you here?

11:43.119 --> 11:45.288
Why I'm a student of

11:43.119 --> 11:45.288
friendship, of course!

11:45.330 --> 11:48.625
Unless you don't think you're

11:45.330 --> 11:48.625
good enough to teach me.

11:48.667 --> 11:51.378
Of course, I am!

11:51.419 --> 11:53.630
No fruit calls in my class.

