[gulp]

11:57.758 --> 12:01.179
Magic is the most important

11:57.758 --> 12:01.179
element of friendship.

12:01.221 --> 12:07.060
So today, I, the Great and

12:01.221 --> 12:07.060
Powerful Trixie, will put on...

12:07.101 --> 12:08.562
a magic show!

12:10.689 --> 12:11.606
[snap]

12:13.900 --> 12:14.859
[squeal]

12:19.656 --> 12:20.532
[whoosh]

12:20.574 --> 12:21.575
[roar]

12:21.616 --> 12:23.201
[screams]

12:23.243 --> 12:27.706
Oh, oh oh, I'm learning

12:23.243 --> 12:27.706
<i>so</i> much, aren't you?

12:27.746 --> 12:29.790
Grr... Discord!

12:34.128 --> 12:35.714
[phone rings]

12:35.754 --> 12:37.424
Hello?

12:37.465 --> 12:40.677
Um, what exactly is a

12:37.465 --> 12:40.677
long-distance plan?

12:41.928 --> 12:45.306
♪♪

12:45.348 --> 12:47.808
Take a lap, team!

12:47.850 --> 12:52.480
Uh, actually, we just finished

12:47.850 --> 12:52.480
Professor Spitfire's workout.

12:52.522 --> 12:55.191
Sounds like somepony

12:52.522 --> 12:55.191
needs a little motivation.

12:55.233 --> 12:57.402
[tweet]

12:57.444 --> 12:58.194
[roar]

12:58.236 --> 12:59.696
[screams]

12:59.738 --> 13:01.573
[growls]

13:01.615 --> 13:04.867
I've never run so

13:01.615 --> 13:04.867
fast in my life.

13:04.909 --> 13:05.910
This is great!

13:08.705 --> 13:09.872
Hey, Coach.

13:09.914 --> 13:11.374
We need a break.

13:11.416 --> 13:13.627
Friendship is about honesty.

13:13.668 --> 13:15.878
So believe me when I say...

13:15.920 --> 13:17.255
We're not stopping!

13:17.297 --> 13:18.256
[tweet]

13:18.298 --> 13:19.966
[gasps]

13:20.007 --> 13:21.301
[roar]

13:21.342 --> 13:23.470
[panicked shouts]

13:23.511 --> 13:27.432
Yona... can't run... faster.

13:29.350 --> 13:30.226
[whimper]

13:30.268 --> 13:31.436
[roar]

13:32.395 --> 13:33.563
[crash]

13:35.273 --> 13:37.442
Discord, that's enough!

13:37.484 --> 13:39.986
Endangering students

13:37.484 --> 13:39.986
crosses the line!

13:40.027 --> 13:42.489
I don't know why you're

13:40.027 --> 13:42.489
trying to ruin this school,

13:42.530 --> 13:43.906
but it stops now.

13:45.408 --> 13:46.284
[zap]

13:46.326 --> 13:48.827
