13:49.912 --> 13:52.206
This is your last warning.

13:52.248 --> 13:54.375
Hey, take it easy, Starlight.

13:54.417 --> 13:56.419
Discord's your friend, remember?

13:56.461 --> 13:58.921
Well, he's not acting like it.

13:58.963 --> 14:00.173
She's right, Discord.

14:00.214 --> 14:01.716
What's your problem?

14:01.758 --> 14:03.301
My problem?

14:03.343 --> 14:06.053
How is the fact that Twilight

14:03.343 --> 14:06.053
decided to put an incompetent,

14:06.095 --> 14:10.849
power-hungry unicorn in charge

14:06.095 --> 14:10.849
of her school my problem?

14:12.101 --> 14:15.104
[blast]

14:17.982 --> 14:20.276
[worried groans]

14:20.318 --> 14:22.529
Ha ha hah.. Don't worry.

14:22.570 --> 14:25.198
I just banished him from

14:22.570 --> 14:25.198
school grounds forever.

14:25.239 --> 14:26.574
He's fine.

14:29.910 --> 14:31.871
That probably made

14:29.910 --> 14:31.871
things worse.

14:31.912 --> 14:33.748
Why didn't you just

14:31.912 --> 14:33.748
talk to Discord?

14:33.790 --> 14:35.834
Because he's right

14:33.790 --> 14:35.834
about one thing.

14:35.875 --> 14:38.837
I've been doing a

14:35.875 --> 14:38.837
terrible job as Headmare.

14:38.878 --> 14:40.171
No, you haven't!

14:40.213 --> 14:42.674
Discord is just

14:40.213 --> 14:42.674
being Discord.

14:42.716 --> 14:44.175
Maybe.

14:44.217 --> 14:47.220
But I wonder why me being in

14:44.217 --> 14:47.220
charge bothers him so much.

14:47.261 --> 14:48.555
[school bell rings]

14:48.596 --> 14:50.724
We can figure that out

14:48.596 --> 14:50.724
after the Spellvenger Hunt.

14:50.765 --> 14:52.225
Come on!

14:52.266 --> 14:55.645
♪♪

14:55.687 --> 14:57.856
For this afternoon's

14:55.687 --> 14:57.856
Spellvenger Hunt,

14:57.938 --> 14:59.858
you'll need to use the

14:57.938 --> 14:59.858
artifacts' history

14:59.899 --> 15:02.819
to find where they're

14:59.899 --> 15:02.819
hidden in the castle.

15:02.861 --> 15:05.530
When you spot one, touch

15:02.861 --> 15:05.530
it with a magic shield

15:05.572 --> 15:07.741
to keep track

15:05.572 --> 15:07.741
of your score.

15:07.782 --> 15:10.618
Twilight left a list of your

15:07.782 --> 15:10.618
hunt partners before she left.

15:10.660 --> 15:12.119
I'll pass out the shields.

15:12.161 --> 15:16.165
♪♪

15:16.207 --> 15:19.377
Ready, set... Spellvenger Hunt!

15:19.419 --> 15:21.962
[excited chatter]

15:22.004 --> 15:24.841
C'mon, we can use Twilight's

15:22.004 --> 15:24.841
observatory to watch the teams!

15:24.883 --> 15:28.803
[chattering]

15:28.845 --> 15:30.513
I hope you know

15:28.845 --> 15:30.513
where you're going.

15:30.555 --> 15:32.515
To the Helm of Yksler!

15:32.557 --> 15:33.767
Eh, works for me.

15:37.771 --> 15:41.315
In our book, it says Yksler

15:37.771 --> 15:41.315
was an honorable Yak warrior.

15:41.357 --> 15:44.985
Any enemies that saw him put

15:41.357 --> 15:44.985
down their weapons in peace.

15:45.027 --> 15:49.031
I think his artifact must be in

15:45.027 --> 15:49.031
one of these suits of armor.

15:53.119 --> 15:54.579
I'm guessing that one.

15:59.208 --> 16:01.878
Yes! One down, five to go!

16:04.714 --> 16:08.509
Aw, Ocellus and Smolder

16:04.714 --> 16:08.509
found their first artifact!

16:08.551 --> 16:09.928
Wait. What's that?

16:12.179 --> 16:13.681
[frightened whimper]

16:13.723 --> 16:16.392
I don't think that's part

16:13.723 --> 16:16.392
of the Spellvenger Hunt.

16:16.434 --> 16:17.811
[screams]

16:17.852 --> 16:19.479
[crash]

16:19.520 --> 16:21.147
The school is haunted!

16:21.188 --> 16:23.357
Not cool!

16:23.399 --> 16:24.567
[gasp]

16:27.445 --> 16:28.613
♪♪

16:28.655 --> 16:31.574
We're totally gonna win

16:28.655 --> 16:31.574
this Spellvenger Hunt!

16:31.616 --> 16:33.660
Yeah, I doubt that.

16:33.701 --> 16:35.787
But at least I know where

16:33.701 --> 16:35.787
one of the artifacts is.

16:35.829 --> 16:37.622
Saw Spike hide it yesterday.

16:42.209 --> 16:44.003
The Crown of Grover!

16:44.044 --> 16:45.254
Score!

16:47.256 --> 16:49.926
They say it's magic, and King

16:47.256 --> 16:49.926
Grover used it to become

16:49.968 --> 16:51.886
the first ruler of Griffonstone.

16:51.928 --> 16:53.513
I know, pretty sweet, right?

16:53.554 --> 16:56.098
You paid attention in class!

16:56.140 --> 16:58.184
What! If you

16:56.140 --> 16:58.184
ever tell an-

16:58.225 --> 17:00.728
[slam]

17:00.770 --> 17:02.772
Whoa! 3-D painting!

17:02.814 --> 17:03.773
[hiss]

17:03.815 --> 17:05.441
[screams]

17:05.483 --> 17:06.484
♪♪

17:06.526 --> 17:07.694
[hiss]

17:07.735 --> 17:09.028
[screams]

17:09.069 --> 17:10.029
♪♪

17:10.070 --> 17:10.864
[hiss]

17:10.905 --> 17:12.198
[screams]

17:12.239 --> 17:17.704
♪♪

17:17.745 --> 17:21.207
Ha ha ha!

17:21.248 --> 17:24.043
Yep, that's definitely Discord.

17:24.084 --> 17:25.753
This is not good.

17:25.795 --> 17:27.672
I thought you banished

17:25.795 --> 17:27.672
him from the school!

17:27.714 --> 17:28.965
Only his body.

17:29.007 --> 17:32.010
Apparently, his ghost can

17:29.007 --> 17:32.010
come and go just fine.

17:32.051 --> 17:34.053
Let's go, we have to stop this.

17:36.764 --> 17:38.599
How? No offense, but

17:36.764 --> 17:38.599
I don't think magic

17:38.641 --> 17:40.226
is the answer

17:38.641 --> 17:40.226
against Discord.

17:40.267 --> 17:43.437
This time, I'm not using magic.

17:45.481 --> 17:46.357
Hmm.

17:46.399 --> 17:47.608
What Yona look for?

17:47.650 --> 17:49.944
The shell of Knuckerbocker.

17:49.986 --> 17:53.823
It's like a seashell, but if you

17:49.986 --> 17:53.823
blow into it, you call a dragon!

17:53.865 --> 17:55.867
There's a sweet poem

17:53.865 --> 17:55.867
in our book about it.

17:55.909 --> 18:00.079
"Climb to the heights with

17:55.909 --> 18:00.079
dragon flight."

18:00.120 --> 18:03.917
Like flight of stairs!

18:03.958 --> 18:05.376
Yona take pony word for it.

18:06.627 --> 18:08.087
[squishy sound]

18:08.128 --> 18:09.296
Huh?

18:09.338 --> 18:11.632
♪♪

18:11.674 --> 18:12.717
[grunts]

18:12.759 --> 18:15.261
What's happening?

18:15.302 --> 18:16.846
Yona not know.

18:16.888 --> 18:20.767
But Yona do know Yona not

18:16.888 --> 18:20.767
like Spellvenger Hunt!

18:20.808 --> 18:23.269
[dramatic music]

18:23.310 --> 18:25.187
Hahaha ha.

18:25.229 --> 18:26.606
Ho ho ho ho!

18:26.647 --> 18:28.148
Ah! Boo Boo-boo!

18:31.485 --> 18:38.076
[yells]

18:38.117 --> 18:44.832
♪♪

18:49.963 --> 18:52.506
Everycreature, stop!

18:52.548 --> 18:55.593
But-but-but the

18:52.548 --> 18:55.593
school is haunted!

18:55.635 --> 18:57.720
It's not haunted; it's Discord.

18:57.762 --> 18:58.763
[poof]

18:59.597 --> 19:01.891
Headmare Starlight!

18:59.597 --> 19:01.891
Look at me, look!

19:01.933 --> 19:03.935
I won the Spellvenger Hunt!

19:03.977 --> 19:05.352
Well, done me!

19:05.394 --> 19:07.063
Now what's my prize?

19:07.105 --> 19:08.856
Detention.

19:08.898 --> 19:11.067
Well, that's disappointing.

19:15.195 --> 19:18.116
Discord, you can't keep

19:15.195 --> 19:18.116
messing up the school.

19:18.157 --> 19:23.079
On the contrary, I think

19:18.157 --> 19:23.079
I rather can, and will.

19:23.121 --> 19:26.165
Then I have just one

19:23.121 --> 19:26.165
thing to say to you.

19:26.206 --> 19:28.417
Do go on.

19:28.459 --> 19:30.252
I'm sorry.

19:30.294 --> 19:31.211
What?

19:31.253 --> 19:33.840
[zap]

19:33.881 --> 19:37.176
I had to stop thinking like a

19:33.881 --> 19:37.176
Headmare and start thinking

19:37.217 --> 19:39.804
like a Guidance Counselor

19:37.217 --> 19:39.804
to finally understand.

19:39.846 --> 19:41.597
You felt left out.

19:41.639 --> 19:45.977
I don't know what

19:41.639 --> 19:45.977
you're getting at.

19:46.019 --> 19:48.729
Nopony ever invited

19:46.019 --> 19:48.729
you to the school.

19:48.771 --> 19:51.649
And when you offered to

19:48.771 --> 19:51.649
help, I didn't listen.

19:51.691 --> 19:54.152
I was so worried about doing

19:51.691 --> 19:54.152
things Twilight's way,

19:54.193 --> 19:57.237
I didn't stop to think

19:54.193 --> 19:57.237
about being a good friend.

19:57.279 --> 19:59.448
I'd like to apologize for that.

19:59.490 --> 20:01.993
And offer you the

19:59.490 --> 20:01.993
job of vice-headmare.

20:02.035 --> 20:03.161
-Huh?

20:02.035 --> 20:03.161
-Really?

20:03.202 --> 20:04.578
-What?

20:03.202 --> 20:04.578
-Why?

20:04.620 --> 20:06.288
Totally confused.

20:07.414 --> 20:08.833
I accept!

20:10.376 --> 20:14.047
I mean, I suppose I can find

20:10.376 --> 20:14.047
some time in my busy schedule

20:14.088 --> 20:15.589
to help you out.

20:15.631 --> 20:18.759
But I will need my own office,

20:15.631 --> 20:18.759
expense account, parking space.

20:18.801 --> 20:22.013
You're new to the world

20:18.801 --> 20:22.013
of education, aren't you?

20:22.055 --> 20:25.516
Next time you want something,

20:22.055 --> 20:25.516
just ask for it, all right?

20:25.558 --> 20:29.395
But then we'd miss out on all

20:25.558 --> 20:29.395
these delightful misadventures.

20:29.436 --> 20:31.898
Hey! Watch the wings!

20:32.398 --> 20:35.401
Now, vice-headmare Discord,

20:32.398 --> 20:35.401
if you'll help me get this

20:35.442 --> 20:37.820
Spellvenger Hunt back in order.

20:37.862 --> 20:38.445
[snap]

20:38.487 --> 20:41.532
Everything is re-hidden.

20:41.574 --> 20:42.867
Ah!

20:42.909 --> 20:46.370
[chuckles] Well, with

20:42.909 --> 20:46.370
a few surprises.

20:47.163 --> 20:48.789
[door crashes open]

20:48.831 --> 20:50.290
Discord!

20:50.332 --> 20:53.252
I can't believe you tricked us

20:50.332 --> 20:53.252
into going on a friendship quest

20:53.293 --> 20:55.088
that wasn't real!

20:55.129 --> 20:57.840
Oh, back so soon?

20:57.882 --> 21:00.384
A glamour spell on

20:57.882 --> 21:00.384
our cutie marks?

21:00.426 --> 21:02.803
A fake summons from the map?

21:02.845 --> 21:04.555
Hey, at least we got

21:02.845 --> 21:04.555
to go spelunking

21:04.597 --> 21:06.182
in that really creepy

21:04.597 --> 21:06.182
cave with all those

21:06.224 --> 21:09.268
eyeless worm

21:06.224 --> 21:09.268
creatures chasing us.

21:09.309 --> 21:12.563
Oh, Yona so glad ponies back.

21:12.605 --> 21:17.026
Uh, y'all get the feelin'

21:12.605 --> 21:17.026
we missed something?

21:17.068 --> 21:19.403
Thanks for taking care

21:17.068 --> 21:19.403
of the school, Starlight.

21:19.445 --> 21:21.530
It was a challenge.

21:21.572 --> 21:23.323
But I think

21:21.572 --> 21:23.323
things turned out

21:23.365 --> 21:25.367
just the way you'd

21:23.365 --> 21:25.367
have handled them.

21:25.409 --> 21:27.995
Guess this means you're

21:25.409 --> 21:27.995
not vice-headmare anymore.

21:28.037 --> 21:31.624
Ooh poo!

21:28.037 --> 21:31.624
I just ordered business cards!

